# Shareable file patterns — engine structure only, no campaign content
# Machine-specific config (template repo path) lives in .template-sync.local (gitignored)
#
# NOT synced (campaign-specific content):
#   meta/worldbuilding.md            — this world's lore; create fresh per campaign
#   meta/mysteries.md                — campaign load-bearing unknowns; create fresh per campaign
#   meta/campaign-design-preferences.md — this group's wishlist; create fresh per campaign
#   meta/party-relationships.md      — this party's bonds; create fresh per campaign
#   data/factions/*, data/locations/*, data/routes/*, data/lore/*, data/characters/*
#   data/items/magic/*               — contains Strahd-specific items
#   data/world-events-pool.md        — campaign event pool
#   historian/*, scheduler/*, maps/* (except maps/CLAUDE.md)
#   tests/commands/*/runs/, tests/commands/*/personas/

